ith <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth was born in 1170, in Hartland, Devon, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 2 sons with Oliver de Dinham."},"et":{"1170–":"1170–Surnud","1170–1221":"1170–1221","1200–1238":"1200–1238","1200–1258":"1200–1258","1170–Female":"1170–Surnud","1238":"1238","1258":"1258","Abt 1200":"umbes 1200","1200":"1200","1221":"1221","abt. 1200":"umbes 1200","1170":"1170","Hartland, Devon, England":"Hartland, Devon, England","of Hartland, Devonshire, England":"Hartland, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1170–":"1170–Kuollut","1170–1221":"1170–1221","1200–1238":"1200–1238","1200–1258":"1200–1258","1170–Female":"1170–Kuollut","1238":"1238","1258":"1258","Abt 1200":"noin 1200","1200":"1200","1221":"1221","abt. 1200":"noin 1200","1170":"1170","Hartland, Devon, England":"Hartland, Devon, England","of Hartland, Devonshire, England":"Hartland, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1170–":"1170–Décédée","1170–1221":"1170–1221","1200–1238":"1200–1238","1200–1258":"1200–1258","1170–Female":"1170–Décédée","1238":"1238","1258":"1258","Abt 1200":"environ 1200","1200":"1200","1221":"1221","abt. 1200":"environ 1200","1170":"1170","Hartland, Devon, England":"Hartland, Devon, Angleterre","of Hartland, Devonshire, England":"Hartland, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth est née en 1170, à Hartland, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 2 fils avec Oliver de Dinham."},"de":{"1170–":"1170–Verstorben","1170–1221":"1170–1221","1200–1238":"1200–1238","1200–1258":"1200–1258","1170–Female":"1170–Verstorben","1238":"1238","1258":"1258","Abt 1200":"um 1200","1200":"1200","1221":"1221","abt. 1200":"um 1200","1170":"1170","Hartland, Devon, England":"Hartland, Devon, England","of Hartland, Devonshire, England":"Hartland, Devon, England, U